0.040     2026-06-22
          - New: `pcg prereqs` / pcg_prereqs (31 MCP tools) -- CPAN dependency hygiene: reconcile
            the DECLARED prerequisites (META.json / MYMETA.json / cpanfile / Makefile.PL, tried in
            that order) against the modules actually use'd / require'd in the indexed code. Flags
            MISSING deps (used but not declared -- add them) and possibly-UNUSED deps (declared but
            never used); core modules (via Module::CoreList) and the project's own packages are
            excluded. A kwalitee-adjacent release check. New Query::prereqs + _declared_prereqs /
            _core_checker; Format::prereqs; CLI `pcg prereqs`.
          - Tests +8 (1086 total): t/83 (Makefile.PL parse, missing/unused classification, and
