            bump from the structural diff vs a git ref: a removed or re-signatured PUBLIC symbol
            forces MAJOR, otherwise new public API is MINOR, otherwise internal-only changes are
            PATCH -- with the evidence listed. A CPAN-release helper that turns the diff you
            already compute into the bump decision. Reuses Diff; new Format::semver; CLI `pcg
