0.038     2026-06-22
          - New: `pcg context <symbol>` / pcg_context (29 MCP tools) -- a paste-ready WORKING
            SET for editing a symbol: the focus symbol(s) WITH verbatim source, their immediate
            callers/callees and covering tests, AND the full source of every PROJECT callee (the
            definitions you must read to change the focus), truncated to a character budget
            (default 16000). A non-symbol arg is treated as a natural-language query resolved via
            semantic (or keyword) search to the focus. The codegraph-for-agents primitive: gather
