            0.030-0.037 wave; stopped after 5 consecutive defect-free passes). Real fixes:
            a `pcg rename` CORRUPTION -- a greedy `->method` match renamed the wrong call on a
            line with two same-named methods (`$self->m($x->m)`), now non-greedy + a regression
            test; Embed `path(Path::Tiny->tempfile)` dropped the File::Temp guard (tempfile
